---
title: Bitter giuseppe
tags: cocktail, bitter, vermouth, cynar, lemon
---

- 2 oz. (60 ml) Cynar
- 1 oz. (30 ml) Cocchi Vermouth di Tornino
- 1/4 oz. (7.5 ml) fresh lemon juice
- 4 dashes Reganâ€™s Orange Bitters No. 6
- 1 swath lemon peel
- Expressed lemon oil and peel for garnish

1. Mix liquids in mixing glass with ice.
1. Stir until well-chilled, about 30 seconds.
1. Strain into a chilled coupe glass.
1. Express lemon oil over the drink and garnish with the swath of lemon peel.
